data.description: Perfect opportunity to own a 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom single-family POOL home in The Acreage, Florida. Situated on a spacious 1.25-acre lot, this property is ideal for all the family. The roof, air conditioning, and impact windows were all updated in 2018. While the home requires a few cosmetic repairs, it is priced to reflect these needs, ensuring value for potential buyers.
